08:32.674 --> 08:35.017
Why are the Lebanese so disruptive?

08:35.737 --> 08:38.901
Because they have to live with uncertainty all the time.

08:39.642 --> 08:41.924
The Egyptians to an extent as well.

08:42.304 --> 08:47.810
But then you go to a country that's maybe more stable, like Kuwait or the Emirates.

08:48.331 --> 08:53.516
And they're less comfortable with uncertainty because they've led a fairly more stable life.

08:54.057 --> 08:57.381
Although everyone in the Middle East today is dealing with uncertainty.

08:58.081 --> 08:59.503
And I think it's a healthy thing.

08:59.703 --> 09:02.386
When you get comfortable with uncertainty,

09:02.754 --> 09:07.219
