09:07.459 --> 09:07.960
Definitely.

09:09.041 --> 09:17.230
And so being out of your comfort zone is so disruptive and it really changes who you are and how you look at life around you.

09:18.232 --> 09:22.697
I worked in the same place for eight years and a half, and I loved them.

09:23.417 --> 09:24.278
They are the...

09:24.298 --> 09:26.201
