09:37.611 --> 09:53.535
It's called Sahabet al-Sa'ada, and it's hosted by an amazing spirit, human being, a Sa'adi ministry, an amazing show presenter, she's an actress, she's a producer, she's an amazing mom, grandmother, I love her.

09:54.076 --> 09:58.162
But I had to leave because I felt that

09:58.370 --> 09:59.872
Yeah, I'm in my comfort zone.

10:00.012 --> 10:02.195
