18:02.215 --> 18:02.536
Great.

18:02.776 --> 18:04.298
And so, no, I did not.

18:04.659 --> 18:06.061
Yeah, no, it's very important.

18:06.682 --> 18:09.426
The ethical use of AI is very important today.

18:09.922 --> 18:11.084
But we need to embrace it.

18:11.284 --> 18:12.045
AI is the future.

18:13.227 --> 18:17.192
We were speaking of something pretty nice and amazing and I want you to explain it.

18:17.252 --> 18:21.157
What's your theory of the Monday and Friday people?

18:22.459 --> 18:29.729
So yeah, in my school I am known for telling people that there's two types of people in the world.

18:29.749 --> 18:30.650
Yeah.

18:30.670 --> 18:33.234
Friday people and Monday people.

18:33.454 --> 18:33.674
Yeah.

18:33.975 --> 18:36.038
Friday people hate what they do all week.

18:36.779 --> 18:39.282
Monday people look forward to Mondays.

18:40.066 --> 18:44.432
In your language, it's Thursday people and Sunday people.

18:44.672 --> 18:45.113
Yeah, true.

18:45.153 --> 18:47.797
80% of the world are Friday people.

18:49.179 --> 18:50.601
