23:13.783 --> 23:14.844
I love this.

23:14.864 --> 23:15.124
Okay.

23:15.545 --> 23:24.914
Tell me a lesson that you actually learned from a person you taught and taught or mentored.

23:25.442 --> 23:31.271
Lesson that I actually learned from a person I taught or mentored.

23:33.454 --> 23:42.508
So I've been an investment banker for 21 years and I did a lot of contracts.

23:43.309 --> 23:54.386
I did a lot of different things where at the end of the day you had sometimes legal documents to protect you.

23:55.298 --> 23:58.562
And about four years ago, I met a student.

23:58.602 --> 23:59.523
She wasn't my student.

23:59.543 --> 24:00.644
She was a master's student.

24:01.485 --> 24:06.071
Um, but I mentored her for a while and we became business partners.

24:07.152 --> 24:18.626
And one of the things she told me was when you have the same values as someone else, you don't really need contracts and things like that.

24:18.666 --> 24:22.450
If you really, really believe that you have the same values and,

24:23.074 --> 24:26.978
We've been business partners now for four years without a contract.

24:27.819 --> 24:28.319
Amazing.

24:28.940 --> 24:30.821
Because we both have the same values.

24:30.962 --> 24:39.189
And finding, I don't recommend this for most people, but finding the right business partner is truly special.

24:40.511 --> 24:42.132
