24:47.037 --> 24:48.018
Have you ever played Monopoly?

24:48.378 --> 24:48.799
Of course.

24:48.839 --> 24:49.800
You're always getting into fights.

24:50.000 --> 24:52.402
Of course.

24:53.922 --> 25:00.789
That is a lesson that I learned that none of the legal documents in any of this stuff in life makes a difference.

25:01.449 --> 25:10.598
When you're dealing with people that have your same values, you don't have to worry about those things.

25:10.618 --> 25:12.981
I love this, and I totally second it.

25:13.001 --> 25:18.526
Which is part of what you were saying earlier, that I don't feel good charging for something like this.

25:19.367 --> 25:22.450
I think it's important to

25:22.818 --> 25:31.969
