26:02.276 --> 26:15.451
And one of the things that we've noticed with AI is when we've surveyed these young people that know how to use AI and use it well, they have, in many cases, they have ethics.

26:16.392 --> 26:16.633
Yes.

26:17.193 --> 26:21.298
Because they realize that if they use AI the wrong way and just

26:21.890 --> 26:26.955
don't think anymore and let AI do all the work and then they get a good grade for not doing it.

26:28.556 --> 26:29.457
They can't do it that way.

26:29.497 --> 26:31.319
They realize that's not them.

26:31.359 --> 26:36.724
And so you find that a lot of these people that really know how to use AI, they have values.

26:37.104 --> 26:39.146
And one of their values is their work ethic.

26:39.907 --> 26:41.108
They don't believe in a free lunch.

26:41.589 --> 26:48.836
They don't believe in that they deserve anything out of the sky, that they have to work for everything that they do.

26:49.716 --> 26:51.378
My father told me when I was a kid,

26:51.810 --> 27:01.042
