29:39.874 --> 29:41.636
And your family has to be number one.

29:42.457 --> 29:43.879
Your family has to be number one.

29:44.700 --> 29:49.425
But health, you know, without health, you can be the luckiest person in the world.

29:49.465 --> 29:53.970
But if you don't have health, no faloose in the world will make up for it.

29:54.391 --> 29:55.172
Yeah.

29:55.192 --> 30:03.622
So I was standing here like the last three days, and I go home, my feet are hurting.

