30:17.494 --> 30:18.676
And I want to be her friend.

30:18.736 --> 30:23.220
And I just say to myself, are you crazy?

30:23.280 --> 30:28.305
You went home yesterday crying because your feet, but at least you were, you were walking.

30:28.925 --> 30:30.166
We take so much for granted.

30:31.047 --> 30:31.287
Yeah.

30:31.688 --> 30:34.090
We take so much for granted.

30:34.110 --> 30:38.194
You know, another lesson my father taught me when he was

30:38.402 --> 30:39.243
about to die.

30:39.844 --> 30:43.970
My father died of liver cancer and he was in his 80s.

30:44.651 --> 30:45.493
