31:23.385 --> 31:34.182
You know, you have to really wake up to the fact that you shouldn't settle, you shouldn't feel bad about, you know, experiences that you have.

31:34.743 --> 31:36.786
It's very important not to have any regrets.

31:37.282 --> 31:39.405
And so you need to live a life of no regrets.

