32:36.578 --> 32:41.604
because I love every moment of this life and I'm grateful for every moment of this life.

32:42.665 --> 32:53.278
And I think that's priceless and that she taught me that and I think it's priceless to really realize that we don't know how many days we have left in our life.

32:54.460 --> 32:58.645
It's not like we're a carton of milk that has an expiration date.

32:58.665 --> 33:03.090
